data.title: Charlotte Bobcats
data.meta_description:
Charlotte Bobcats forward Gerald Wallace (3) gives a hi-five to teammate and guard Brevin Knight (22) after their team forced a turnover in the first quarter against the Boston Celtics in the new Charlotte Bobcats Arena on Saturday, November 5, 2005. The Bobcats defeated the Celtics in overtime 107-105 in front of 19,026 fans. 
	
	Foto Copyrighted by YMJames and The Charlotte Observer.
